description: These dongers are exclaiming WOW, which is also simply written in superscript English letters. They all have wide open mouths as if they are saying or gasping “wow!” This also shows their surprise. Here’s the word if you just want to copy only the WOW: ꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ (ᵒ̤̑ ₀̑ ᵒ̤̑)wow!*✰ !(ᵒ̤̑ ◁ ᵒ̤̑)wow!৹ᢄᵍᵎᵎ (⑅ ॣ•͈૦•͈ ॣ)꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ ˶⍤⃝˶꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ ꒰⑅ ॣ•͈૦•͈ ॣ꒱໊꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ ʸᵉᵃʰᵎᵎ े ̡̡⍤⃝  ̢̢ेे ꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎ ╰║ ❛ ◯ ❛ ║╯꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ （◎0◎）꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ (இ௦இ)꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ (๑o̴̶̷̥᷅﹏o̴̶̷̥᷅๑)꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ ༼⁰o⁰；༽꒳ᵒ꒳ᵎᵎᵎ
title: WOW!
